COMPONENT NAME: LKM Oracle BI to Oracle (DBLINK
AUTHOR: Oracle
DESCRIPTION - Loading Knowledge Module - Loads data from any Oracle BI physical layer to an Oracle target database using dblink. - This module creates synonyms for the target staging table and uses the OBIEE populate command which directly populates the target staging table.
REQUIREMENTS - A DBLink must be created from the Fusion Transaction DB to the target Oracle database and this DBLink name must be specified in the target dataserver connection.
- Requires a Oracle BI data server with the folowwing JDBC property: NQ_SESSION.SELECTPHYSICAL = yes
BASIC CONFIGURATION Requires a Oracle BI data server with the folowwing JDBC property: NQ_SESSION.SELECTPHYSICAL = yes
OPTIONS (Refer to Option descriptions for more information on each option) OBIEE_SQL_PREFIX : This can be set with any valid OBIEE sql prefix. For e.g, set variable EFFECTIVE_DATE='2008-10-01' LOG_FILE_NAME : Log File Name.
Set this option to NO if you wish to retain temporary objects (files and scripts) after integration. Useful for debugging.

<% if ("C".equals(odiRef.getJrnInfo( "JRN_METHOD"))) { %> /* Consistant journalization detected. */ /* Lock should be done by a specific step in a package */ <% } else { %> update <%=odiRef.getTable( "L" , "JRN_NAME" , "A" )%> set JRN_CONSUMED = '1' where (1=1) <%=odiRef.getJrnFilter()%> <% } %>

dropCmd = """EXECUTE PHYSICAL CONNECTION POOL <?=odiRef.getFlexFieldValue(odiRef.getInfo("SRC_CONNECT_GUID"),"1400","OBIEE_CONNECTION_POOL")?> drop synonym <%=odiRef.getInfo("COLL_NAME")%>"""
prepDropStmt = srcCon.prepareStatement(dropCmd)
prepDropStmt.executeQuery()

createCmd = """EXECUTE PHYSICAL CONNECTION POOL <?=odiRef.getFlexFieldValue(odiRef.getInfo("SRC_CONNECT_GUID"),"1400","OBIEE_CONNECTION_POOL")?> create synonym <%=odiRef.getInfo( "COLL_NAME")%> for <%=odiRef.getTable("R", "COLL_NAME", "W")%>"""
prepCreateStmt = srcCon.prepareStatement(createCmd)
prepCreateStmt.executeQuery()

loadCmd = """ <%String fromClause;%> <%fromClause=odiRef.getFrom();%> <%java.util.regex.Pattern pat = java.util.regex.Pattern.compile("(\s+)select(\s+)|(\s+)SELECT(\s+)|(\()select(\s+)|(\()SELECT(\s+)");%> <%java.util.regex.Matcher mat = pat.matcher(fromClause);%> <%fromClause=mat.replaceAll("$1$3$5$7select_physical$2$4$6$8");%> <%=odiRef.getOption("OBIEE_SQL_PREFIX")%> POPULATE <%=odiRef.getInfo("COLL_NAME")%> MODE (APPEND TABLE CONNECTION POOL <?=odiRef.getFlexFieldValue(odiRef.getInfo("SRC_CONNECT_GUID"),"1400","OBIEE_CONNECTION_POOL")?>) as select_physical <%=odiRef.getPop("DISTINCT_ROWS")%> <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[EXPRESSION]\t[ALIAS_SEP] [CX_COL_NAME]", ",\n\t", "", "")%> from <%=fromClause%> where (1=1) <%=odiRef.getFilter()%> <%=odiRef.getJrnFilter()%> <%=odiRef.getJoin()%> <%=odiRef.getGrpBy()%> <%=odiRef.getHaving()%> """
prepLoadStmt = srcCon.prepareStatement(loadCmd)
prepLoadStmt.executeQuery()

<% if ("C".equals(odiRef.getJrnInfo( "JRN_METHOD"))) { %> /* Consistant journalization detected. */ /* Lock should be done by a specific step in a package */ <% } else { %> delete from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","JRN_NAME","A")%> where JRN_CONSUMED = '1' <%=odiRef.getJrnFilter()%> <% } %>

dropCmd = """EXECUTE PHYSICAL CONNECTION POOL <?=odiRef.getFlexFieldValue(odiRef.getInfo("SRC_CONNECT_GUID"),"1400","OBIEE_CONNECTION_POOL")?> drop synonym <%=odiRef.getInfo("COLL_NAME")%>"""
prepDropStmt = srcCon.prepareStatement(dropCmd)
prepDropStmt.executeQuery()
